::\n<br><br>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n:::: {.panel-tabset .nav-pills}\n\n## Prison Population\n<center>\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div id=\"body-section\">\n<br/>\n<div id=\"big-section-title\">Admission Types</div>\n<br/>\n<div id=\"regular-text\">Prison populations are shaped by two primary groups: new court commitments, or individuals newly incarcerated for a criminal offense, and parole returns/revocations, those who return to prison for failing to meet the conditions of their parole. Understanding the relative proportion of these two groups is pivotal for evaluating the effectiveness of a state's criminal justice policies.</div>\n<br/>\n<div id=\"visualization\">No Data</div>\n<br/>\n<div id=\"visualization\">No Data</div>\n<br/>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div id=\"body-section\">\n<br/>\n<div id=\"big-section-title\">Prison Population Trends</div>\n<br/>\n<div id=\"regular-text\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.</div>\n<br/>\n<div id=\"visualization\">\n<div class=\"highchart html-widget html-fill-item-overflow-hidden html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-cca18b2469f9e7d2f2f8\" style=\"width:100%;height:500px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-cca18b2469f9e7d2f2f8\">{\"x\":{\"hc_opts\":{\"chart\":{\"reflow\":true},\"title\":{\"text\":\"Trends in Prison Population, Releases to Parole, and Parole Eligibility from 2010 to 2020\"},\"yAxis\":{\"title\":{\"text\":null},\"labels\":{\"format\":\"{value:,.0f}\"}},\"credits\":{\"enabled\":false},\"exporting\":{\"enabled\":true},\"boost\":{\"enabled\":false},\"plotOptions\":{\"series\":{\"label\":{\"enabled\":fal