ison to parole pulled from Annual Parole Survey (2010-2018), eligible for parole pulled from NCRP data (2010-2020).</div>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div id=\"body-section\">\n<br/>\n<div id=\"big-section-title\">Who's in Prison?</div>\n<br/>\n<div id=\"regular-text\">The following visualizations offer an overview of the demographic composition of the prison population by race and ethnicity, gender, and age.</div>\n<br/>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.panel-tabset}\n### Race and Ethinicity\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div id=\"body-section\">\n<br/>\n<div id=\"visualization\">No Data</div>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n:::\n\n\n### Gender\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div id=\"body-section\">\n<br/>\n<div id=\"visualization\">No Data</div>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n:::\n\n\n### Age\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div id=\"body-section\">\n<br/>\n<div id=\"visualization\">No Data</div>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n:::\n\n:::\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div id=\"body-section\">\n<br/>\n<div id=\"big-section-title\">Sentence Length</div>\n<br/>\n<div id=\"regular-text\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.</div>\n<br/>\n<div id=\"visualization\">No Data</div>\n<div id=\"visualization\">No Data</div>\n<br/>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div id=\"body-section\">\n<br/>\n<div id=\"big-section-title\">Criminal Offense</div>\n<br/>\n<div id=\"regular-text\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim ven